Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.680796123712835, \"rank\": 0.46880354001916275, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trans Nzoia police commander Jeremiah Ole Kosiom said thatCheptegei's boyfriend bought a can of petrol, poured it on her and set her on fireduring a disagreement on Sunday.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trans Nzoia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"score\": 0.9668004285495062, \"rank\": 0.03433963005945733, \"text\": \"Jeremiah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremiah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ndiema was also said to have sustained burn wounds.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police say both are receiving specialised treatment at the Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital in Eldoret city.\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete was reported to be in a critical condition.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking outside of hospital, the athlete's father Joseph Cheptegei told reporters: \\\"They were just friends and I wonder why he wanted to take away things belonging to my daughter.\\\"\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\", \"score\": 0.9128703948332587, \"rank\": 0.09544494532968253, \"text\": \"Joseph\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told Kenyan newspaper The Star that the Olympian has two children whose father is a different person living in Uganda.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999987345330559, \"rank\": 4.3035887540826484e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4350817996488292e-19, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Cheptegei said the marathon runner's daughters aged nine and 11, who were at church when the attack happened, were in agony and under the care their grandmother Agnes Ndiema, Kenyan newspaper The Standard reported.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish to state that my wounded daughter is married and her husband is in Uganda.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4350817996488292e-19, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her attacker was a friend they met in Kenya and my daughter trusted him.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.443734113335076e-19, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They fell out recently but the suspect sneaked into her compound on Sunday afternoon, armed with five litres of petrol and hid in a poultry house,\\\" he claimed.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rebecca was outside the house when the suspect appeared and immediately poured petrol on her before lighting the fire.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.680796123712835, \"rank\": 0.46880354001916275, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My daughter called for help by asking her sister who was in the home to bring a blanket to put off the fire but the suspect who was armed with a machete chased her away and Rebecca burnt.\\\"\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.680796123712835, \"rank\": 0.46880354001916275, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The father went on to claim\\u00a0that\\u00a0Cheptegei and the suspect had a case which was being investigated by the\\u00a0Directorate of Criminal Investigations (DCI) in Kenya.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_inspector\", \"score\": 0.9999989053541491, \"rank\": 1.0946468177454207e-06, \"text\": \"DCI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_inspector\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_inspector\"}, {\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.44